ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbb4a74c10518f4473e546d9165fe16d1ed36a1","tid":297004,"uid":60709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:24:47.000Z","msg":"幼稚園後樓梯果集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5e2f71b4f4ba847fb39292210e71340ce5a6c6","tid":297004,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:26:16.000Z","msg":"妮妮隻兔<br />\n小葵大個咗，都好恐怖"},{"pid":"2b199055fb11892e643b8478bcddd874867afabe","tid":297004,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:31:07.000Z","msg":"留名睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5809920a019cd3bb8362a51173d37507955c9717","tid":297004,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幼稚園後樓梯果集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頂見到結局心都寒一寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85fd49bc2c5e74de51d75b8526bdadf82deed12","tid":297004,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0df8fd49985671ebf11319613ce6237f5a114c4","tid":297004,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我記得漫畫好似有畫佢阿爸阿媽啪啪啪</blockquote><br />\n有。漫畫第一期<br />\n畫埋佢老豆扯旗</blockquote><br />\n求link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咁撚痴線咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似扑扑下小新入左去間房<br />\n點知原來小新夢遊<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果隻係講美雅買左情趣內衣引老廣志扑野<br />\n當佢地想攬埋一齊，跟住小新同小葵突然出現<br />\n問佢地做咩，美雅扮野話做晚操，廣志就話社區捧球賽就開始要練習衝壘<br />\n跟住兩兄妹去睇電視，美雅就話趕佢地去訓，叫廣志等佢一陣<br />\n廣志等左好耐見重未得就去睇下咩事，原來美雅掛住睇電視<br />\n跟住本身廣志想熄電視，結果睇埋一份<br />\n最後真係到訓教時間，小新同小葵係房訓<br />\n兩公婆就係隔離房除晒衫準備扑野<br />\n結果小新無啦啦夢遊走左入黎，兩公婆即刻呢入張庇<br />\n小新拎左美雅條底褲當帽跟住就話去痾屎<br />\n兩公婆話小新痾屎要痾成半個鐘大把時間<br />\n點知小葵入埋黎拎左佢地個condom放係頭就走左<br />\n兩公婆就為左呢兩個細路而笑<br />\n完。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 最愛小新，睇到識背(漫畫only)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但當你睇到我咁熟就好少會翻睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為你睇第一格已經記得後面講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話，小新動畫平時一係唔講鬼，一講就好鬼恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XFHjl7pF9NY&amp;list=PLkxUbYIgXJqLzXUkdo9ASd0K3w5j7DJRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXFHjl7pF9NY%26list%3DPLkxUbYIgXJqLzXUkdo9ASd0K3w5j7DJRU&d=lkD6EmgsIG4G%2FZMb9TgwzF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3f5c362b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XFHjl7pF9NY&amp;list=PLkxUbYIgXJqLzXUkdo9ASd0K3w5j7DJRU</a>&amp;list=PLkxUbYIgXJqLzXUkdo9ASd0K3w5j7DJRU<br />\n<br />\n第二個故事，最後嚇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n13:19</blockquote><br />\n好慘無人理你，i know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c2e78fb4404fd6a2d3dcef2b194f74b50c350f","tid":297004,"uid":119853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"31934edc569850c9c085a1d88a0d0f3fc8669243","tid":297004,"uid":14957,"like